{"tid":380023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係唔明馮文樂點解紅唔起","createTime":"2017-08-29T20:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T20:51:20.000Z","uid":77721,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b20bb1173890d246d67353f562437b470ca1d630","tid":380023,"uid":77721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:02:38.000Z","msg":"係人都知馮文樂扮聲專家 無論克勤校長定學友都扮到有9成似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n殘酷一叮比賽片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C4ax5g56t78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC4ax5g56t78&d=8z1brvdlsQg%2B6kaZjdJoAqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e20f3d13\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C4ax5g56t78</a><br />\n<br />\n最近係youtube睇到馮文樂用自己把聲唱歌 發現真係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講技巧 佢勝過好多依家所謂嘅歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔知係咪把聲唔夠特別所以紅唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馮文樂真聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U5WAUtamKgs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU5WAUtamKgs&d=8z1brvdlsQg%2B6kaZjdJoAqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a3dd7cc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U5WAUtamKgs</a><br />\n<br />\n真係好希望香港人可以捧返啲真係有實力嘅歌手 而唔係一啲上台唱歌都唔夠氣嘅偽毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649d314f3ac038b59d3005cd709da9e17840587c","tid":380023,"uid":68448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:04:42.000Z","msg":"唔係話呢條友響大陸搵夠真銀收左山喇咩"},{"pid":"3f8f1f18e4576263801ae10683d8955d79eb887b","tid":380023,"uid":77721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3407e61949da7b41b743b91662e6946801d8464","tid":380023,"uid":19072,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-2